    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-8032-9d42-e288799f9e91",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Course Load Analytics is a more accurate representation of course-work than credit hours. The study uses data from course catalogs of a public university and create a machine-learning model meant to predict course-load ratings. Analysis of results shows that students experiencing greater course-load are more likely to dropout - especially in STEM and other fields that have a very high pre-requisite burden of knowledge. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-8032-9d42-e288799f9e91",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "eca0c756-cace-4359-ae29-ca4daa4bd057"
        },
